# Rafter promo color grade — minimal 2-point LUT
# Lifts shadows slightly, pulls midtones toward teal, accentuates the green channel
# enough that the rafter brand color (#2ea44f) reads correctly across YouTube/Instagram
# compression. Generated by hand to keep the file readable; replace with a properly
# graded .cube from DaVinci if a colorist later wants to refine.

TITLE "Rafter Promo Grade v0"
LUT_3D_SIZE 2
DOMAIN_MIN 0.0 0.0 0.0
DOMAIN_MAX 1.0 1.0 1.0

# 8 corners of the unit cube, R,G,B (shadow lift +0.02, green channel +0.04 in mids):
0.020 0.020 0.020
0.940 0.040 0.040
0.040 0.980 0.060
0.940 0.940 0.060
0.040 0.040 0.940
0.940 0.060 0.940
0.060 0.940 0.940
0.940 0.940 0.940
